  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-6bebf5ffddce",
  "content": "### OTel Spans\n### Metrics\n\n### Structured Log Events\n\n```\nchunking_started         — INFO, file_path + extension + strategy_name\nchunking_completed       — INFO, chunks_produced + splits + merges + token_stats\nchunking_oversized       — WARN, chunk exceeds budget, triggering split\nchunking_fallback        — WARN, no strategy found, using FallbackChunker\n```\n\n\n### ProcessingReport (returned to caller)\n\n```rust\npub struct ProcessingReport {\n    pub files_processed: usize,\n    pub total_chunks: usize,\n    pub chunks_split: usize,\n    pub chunks_merged: usize,\n    pub token_stats: TokenStats,\n    pub per_strategy: HashMap<String, StrategyStats>,\n}\n\npub struct TokenStats {\n    pub min: usize,\n    pub max: usize,\n    pub mean: usize,\n    pub median: usize,\n}\n\npub struct StrategyStats {\n    pub files: usize,\n    pub chunks: usize,\n    pub splits: usize,\n    pub merges: usize,\n}\n```\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-02-m3.3-embedding-chunking-design.md",
